Sri Lanka Telecom to Spend 6 Billion Rupees for Digital Network

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 
2011-07-19T11:11:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/sri-lanka-telecom-to-spend-6-billion-rupees-for-digital-network.html
     July 19 (Bloomberg) -- Sri Lanka Telecom Plc (SLTL)  plans to spend
6 billion rupees over the next two years to fully migrate to a
digital network, Chief Executive Officer Greg Young said in
 Colombo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
